race.comment: CRASHMYPLAYA (5) deep into the preparation now and will appreciate the extra distance. Surged late with an eye-catching second over 1500m at Port Macquarie. On the quick backup and can finally get off the mark. CAIRO QUEEN (4) fifth-up today with the claim and can pinch some cheap sectionals early from the good gate. Taken to the front when collared late for a narrow second over 1540m at the Gold Coast Poly. Gets her chance to run this trip out. Each way. ADEEL IT'S A STEAL (1) improving Dundeel gelding getting out to his right trip today. Better effort second-up when closed strongly to secure third over 1515m at Coffs Harbour. Shouldered the big weight last start and shouldn't be a Maiden for long. MAHUIKA MAROI (2) much better performance at her second run back when stalked the speed for a tough second over 1700m at this track. Can get cover from the draw and take a hand in the finish.
